title.rendered: Cleanstar Ghibli T1 Backpack Vacuum Cleaner 1450w

content.rendered:
One machine can do it all! Can be used on any surface – staircase, around the house & small areas. This is truly a multi-purpose machine.

  • Designed to strip, wax, buff, polish, sand & refinish your hard surface floors such as marble, tiles, vinyl, wood and more.
  • Can even dry clean your carpets so you can use them

immediately.

  • 250 Watt power (240v)
  • 13″ working width
  • 150rpm working speed
  • Gross weight: 14.8kg
  • Comes with: Soft Brush, Hard Brush, Pad Holder, Polishing

Pad, Microfibre Pad.
